<Turn speaker="spk2" startTime="455.732" endTime="508.104" fidelity="high">
<Sync time="455.732"/>
Ja, res smo tudi mi malo obstali. 
<Sync time="458.089"/>
#Eee, a le za trenutek, zato ker smo vedeli, da 
<Sync time="460.768"/>
